[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]8月31日早上6点，本季首场风暴在[[佛得角|佛得角]]附近出现。气旋起初是热带风暴，在向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]移动期间缓慢增强，于9月1日达到飓风强度。风暴蜿蜒向西北移动，于9月2日进一步强化成二级飓风。气旋继续向西北前进，再于9月6日晚转向东北。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}次日上午11点30分左右，风暴达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时155公里、最低[[气压|气压]]972[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.7[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度。9月9日清晨，气旋强度回落到一级飓风标准，然后于当天在[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]以北较远处海域转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。风暴的温带残留继续减弱，最终于9月10日在[[爱尔兰岛|爱尔兰岛]]以西洋面逐渐消散。<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | deadurl = no }}</ref>据“圣彼得号”（{{lang|en|St. Peter}}）[[三桅帆船|三桅帆船]]的船员报告，有一艘载有45人的船倾覆，无人生还<ref name="partagas">{{cite report | accessdate = 2016-12-04 | location = Miami, Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100601171821/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1894-1897/1897.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1894-1897/1897.pdf | title = Year 1897 | author1 = Jose Fernandez-Partagas | author2 = Henry Diaz | date = 1996 | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | pages = 57–69 | archivedate = 2010-06-01 }}</ref><ref name="deadliest">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pastdeadly.shtml | title = The Deadliest Atlantic Tropical Cyclones, 1492-1996 | author1 = Edward N. Rappaport | author2 = Jose Fernandez-Partagas | date = 1997-04-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160809035651/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pastdeadly.shtml | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | pages = 57–69 | accessdate = 2016-12-04 | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-08-09 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。
